e:90%;\"></span>\n| &amp;#x10D30;||&amp;#x10D31;||&amp;#x10D32;||&amp;#x10D33;||&amp;#x10D34;||&amp;#x10D35;||&amp;#x10D36;||&amp;#x10D37;||&amp;#x10D38;||&amp;#x10D39;\n|}{{clear}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Rohingya people]]\n[[Category:Alphabets]]\n[[Category:Writing systems of Asia]]\n[[Category:Writing systems introduced in 1980]]\n[[Category:Scripts encoded in Unicode]]\n[[Category:Arabic script]]\n\n\n{{writingsystem-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox writing system\n| name = Hanifi Rohingya script\n| altname = \ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd07\ud803\udd25\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd1a\ud803\udd12\ud803\udd19\ud803\udd1d \ud803\udd07\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd15\ud803\udd1e\ud803\udd09\ud803\udd1e \ud803\udd13\ud803\udd20\ud803\udd11\ud803\udd24\ud803\udd1d<ref name=omniglot />\n| languages = [[Rohingya language]]\n| type = Alphabet\n| unicode = [https://www.unicode.org/charts/PDF/U10D00.pdf U+10D00\u2013U+10D3F]\n| iso15924 = Rohg\n| sample =\n| note =\n}}\n\nThe '''Hanifi Rohingya script''' is a unified script for the [[Rohingya language]]. Rohingya was first written in the 19th century with a version of the [[Arabic script|Perso-Arabic script]]. In 1975, an orthographic Arabic script was developed, based on the [[Urdu alphabet]].\n\nIn the 1980s, [[Mohammad Hanif (scholar)|Mohammad Hanif]] and his colleagues created the suitable [[phonetic script]] based on Arabic letters; it has been compared to the [[N\u2019ko]] script. The script also includes a set of decimal numbers.<ref name=\"omniglot\">{{cite web|url=https://www.omniglot.com/writing/rohingya.htm|title=Rohingya alphabets, pronunciation and language|website=[[Omniglot]]|publisher=Simon Ager|access-date=9 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://skyknowledge.com/rohingya.htm |title=Hanifi alphabet for Rohingya |last=James |first=Ian |date=5 July 2012 |website=Sky Knowledge |publisher= |access-date=9 October 2017 |quote=}}</ref>\n\n===Keyboard===\n[[File:Rohingya-Keyboard-online.jpg|thumb|375px|Layout of the Rohingya virtual keyboard.]]\nA virtual keyboard was developed by [[Google]] for the Rohingya language in 2019 and allows users to type directly in the Rohingya script. The Rohingya Unicode keyboard layout can be found [https://languagetools-153419.appspot.com/rhg/ here].\n\n==Character==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Rohingya alphabets -29\n|-\n! colspan=6 | \ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd07\ud803\udd25\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd1a\ud803\udd12\ud803\udd19\ud803\udd1d \ud803\udd07\ud803\udd25\ud803\udd21\ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd09\ud803\udd22<ref>{{Cite web | title=Rohingya Language Academy | url=https://www.rohingyazuban.com/}}</ref>\n|-\n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| \ud803\udd05||\ud803\udd04||\ud803\udd03||\ud803\udd02||\ud803\udd01||\ud803\udd00\n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| \ud803\udd0b||\ud803\udd0a||\ud803\udd09||\ud803\udd08||\ud803\udd07||\ud803\udd06      \n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| \ud803\udd11||\ud803\udd10||\ud803\udd0f||\ud803\udd0e||\ud803\udd0d||\ud803\udd0c\n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| \ud803\udd17||\ud803\udd16||\ud803\udd15||\ud803\udd14||\ud803\udd13||\ud803\udd12\n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| ||\ud803\udd1c||\ud803\udd1b||\ud803\udd1a||\ud803\udd19||\ud803\udd18 \n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Rohingya vowels -7\n|-\n! colspan=6 | \ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd07\ud803\udd25\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd1a\ud803\udd12\ud803\udd19\ud803\udd1d \ud803\udd00\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd09\ud803\udd21\ud803\udd0c \ud803\udd00\ud803\udd1e\ud803\udd09\ud803\udd21\ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd22<ref>{{Cite web | title=Rohingya Zuban | url=https://www.rohingyazuban.com/}}</ref>\n|- \n|-align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| \ud803\udd22||\ud803\udd21||\ud803\udd20||\ud803\udd1f||\ud803\udd1e||\ud803\udd1d\n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| ||\u25cc\ud803\udd27||\u25cc\ud803\udd26||\u25cc\ud803\udd25||\u25cc\ud803\udd24||\ud803\udd23       \n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Rohingya numerals\n|-\n! colspan=10 | \ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd07\ud803\udd25\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd1a\ud803\udd12\ud803\udd19\ud803\udd1d \ud803\udd13\ud803\udd21\ud803\udd14\ud803\udd01\ud803\udd21\ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd22<ref>{{Cite web | title=Rohingya Zuban Academy | url=https://www.rohingyazuban.com/}}</ref>\n|-\n|- align=center | <span style=\"font-size:200%;\"></span>\n| \ud803\udd30 || \ud803\udd31 || \ud803\udd32 || \ud803\udd33 || \ud803\udd34 || \ud803\udd35 || \ud803\udd36 || \ud803\udd37 || \ud803\udd38 || \ud803\udd39\n|}\n\n== Pronunciation ==\n=== Alphabet ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ \n|- \n! Character !! Name !! Final !! Medial !! Pronunciation !! Unicode <ref>{{Cite web | title=Rohingya Language | url=https://www.rohingyazuban.com/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | title=Unicode 11.0.0 | url=https://www.unicode.org/versions/Unicode11.0.0/ | publisher=[[Unicode Consortium]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| <span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd00</span> || | A ||<span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd00</span>|| || |{{IPA|/\u0254/, /\u0294/}} || | U+10D00\n|-\n| <span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd01</span> || | BA ||<span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd01\ud803\udd22</span>||<span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\"> \u0640\ud803\udd01\u0640 </span>|| |{{IPA|/b/}} || | U+10D01\n|-\n| <span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd02</span> || | PA ||<span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd02\ud803\udd22</span>||<span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\"> \u0640\ud803\udd02\u0640 </span>|| |{{IPA|/p/}} || | U+10D02\n|-\n| <span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\ud803\udd03</span> || | TA ||<span style=\"font-size:x-large;line-height:24pt\">\